fields.name: CommCare Connect Child Health Campaign
fields.description: High-need child health interventions for children under 5

fields.title: CommCare Connect Child Health Campaign (CCC-CHC) - Expression of Interest
fields.description: We are seeking partners to deliver door-to-door child health services including vitamin A supplementation, deworming tablets distribution, malnutrition screening, vaccine status checking, and ORS/Zinc drop-off for diarrhea management.
fields.scope_of_work: Door-to-door delivery of vitamin A, deworming tablets, malnutrition screening using MUAC measurements, vaccine checking and referrals, ORS/Zinc distribution for diarrhea cases, real-time data entry via CommCare Connect smartphone app
